title: Conor McGregor denies sexual assault at NBA game
description: Conor McGregor has denied allegations of sexual assault against a woman at game four of the NBA finals on Saturday.

title: Iceland stores in Ireland ordered to recall imported frozen animal products
description: The Irish arm of supermarket Iceland has been ordered to remove imported frozen animal products from its stores.

title: Tourist dies after being 'pushed' down ravine near 'Disney' castle
description: An American man has been arrested after a tourist fell to her death near a German beauty spot said to have inspired a famous Disney castle.

title: British man fears his relatives among the missing after migrant boat sinks
description: A British man has told Sky News he fears his relatives are among the hundreds who are missing after a fishing boat overloaded with migrants sank off the coast of Greece.

title: Migration across the Mediterranean is a brutal throw of the dice
description: There is a lottery within the boats that take the migrant route across the Mediterranean.

title: Eurozone interest rate at more than 20-year high
description: The interest rate in the 20 Eurozone countries has been hiked to a more than 20-year high.

title: 3,000-year-old mummy found in Peru
description: A mummy approximately 3,000 years old has been found in Lima, Peruvian archaeologists have said.

title: Dances With Wolves actor faces further sex assault charges
description: Dances With Wolves actor Nathan Chasing Horse has been charged with new sex crimes in Canada in the latest criminal case brought against him.

title: Hundreds feared dead as search continues for missing migrants in boat disaster
description: A massive search operation is continuing for "hundreds" of missing migrants after at least 78 drowned when a fishing boat sank off the coast of Greece.

title: Beyonce blamed for surprise rise in inflation in Sweden
description: Two concerts performed by Beyonce in Stockholm last month may have caused Swedish inflation to rise, a senior economist has suggested.

title: Nick Kyrgios reveals he contemplated suicide after 2019 Wimbledon loss
description: Nick Kyrgios has revealed he ended up in a psychiatric ward following a loss at Wimbledon in 2019 because he felt suicidal.
